OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew public buildings must  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhave separate male and     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffemale toilets, says       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has said it wants all   
OL,6, new public buildings in England to have
OL,7, separate male and female toilets.      
OL,9,FEqualities minister Kemi Badenoch said 
OL,10,Fit was "vital that women feel safe" and
OL,11,F"that their needs are respected".      
OL,13,FThe "rise in gender-neutral toilets"   
OL,14,Fmeant female users had felt "unfairly  
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged" and faced longer queues,
OL,16,Fthe government added.                  
OL,18,FBut transgender rights groups argue    
OL,19,Fgender-neutral toilets can protect     
OL,20,Ftrans people from discrimination.      
